1. *Ceš* li doći? (Will you come?)
2. *Ceš* li se vratiti? (Will you come back?)
3. *Ceš* li nam pomoći? (Will you help us?)
4. Ono što *ceš* činiti zavisi od tebe. (What you will do depends on you.)
5. *Ceš* li imati odgovor? (Will you have an answer?)
6. Ko *ceš* biti? (Who will you be?)
7. Koju lekciju *ceš* učiti? (Which lesson will you learn?)
8. *Ceš* li biti tu? (Will you be there?)
9. Kada *ceš* krenuti? (When will you start?)
10. Šta *ceš* raditi? (What will you do?)